            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPhoenician\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPhoenician', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Texto fenicio presente en el Museo Británico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite0> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBanner\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBanner', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Banner en estilo semejante al encontrado en la tumba de Wu Zetian (武則天). © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite1>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAtra\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAtra', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tablet Babilónico sobre el Diluvio. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite2>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBuda\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBuda', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">El Tablet del Diluvio. © Trustees of the British Museum ().</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">5 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBritishMuseum0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBritishMuseum0', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cesta oblonga de junco trenzado. © Trustees of the British Museum (). Shared under a <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a>.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">6 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGilgamesh\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGilgamesh', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Lista de Reyes de Abydos. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite3>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">7 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgMid001\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMid001', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Diferentes tipos de vasos, expuestos en el Museo Británico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite4> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">8 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEgypt\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEgypt', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cilindro de Ciro. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite5> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">9 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPottery1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPottery1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Mapa del mundo habitable. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite6>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">10 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCylinder\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCylinder', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tablilla encontrada en Tell Al-'Ubaid. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite7>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">11 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgB', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Astrolabio que muestra un calendario con los meses en latín, conservado en el Museo Británico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite8> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">12 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgT1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgT1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Moneda de la dinastía Tang del año <htdate0>, en el Museo Británico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite9> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">13 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAstro\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAstro', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"><i>Épico de Lugalbanda</i>. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite10>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">14 / 26</div><img class=\"img